Instalar
 - Django
 - Python 2.7
 - PostgreSQL (o el que se quiera)
 - Scrapy
		pip2 install Scrappy

		Posiblemente haya que darle permisos del lectura al fichero de tipos del scrapy
		chmod +r /usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/Scrapy-0.16.4-py2.7.egg/scrapy/mime.types

 - Beautiful Soup python2-beautifulsoup4
		pip2 install beautifulsoup4

		En arch linux instalar desde los paquetes
		pacman -S python2-beautifulsoup4

 - Dyject. Rependency injection
		pip2 install dyject

		Aglyph
		http://www.ninthtest.net/aglyph-python-dependency-injection/

 - Hunspell https://www.archlinux.org/packages/extra/any/hunspell-es/files/

PyEnchant   pacman -S hunspell-en hunspell-es

pytidylib   HTML Tidy apt-get install libtidy-0.99-0

apt-get install enchant myspell-es libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev python-dev libtidy-0.99-0

Al crear la base de datos
python2.7 manage.py syncdb
python2.7 manage.py check_permissions

